OpenCalais PHP Demo Package README

In the package you will find the following directories:

doc 		- Installation and User Guide in Microsoft Word format
src\public 	- HTML, PHP and JavaScript files to be placed on a public directory on your Web server
src\pear 	- the PEAR JSON package to be installed on your Web server
LICENSE		- BSD license file
READEM		- this file

INSTALLATION:
Please refer to the Installation document under doc
